# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the swiss fund for needy victims of the holocaust has transferred ## million swiss francs -lrb- about ##.# million u.s. dollars -rrb- to the world jewish restitution organization <unk> -rrb- in jerusalem for the support of jewish holocaust survivors in eastern europe and the former soviet union .

(t / transfer-01
      :ARG0 (f / fund
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Switzerland"))
            :purpose (p / person
                  :ARG1-of (v / victimize-01
                        :ARG0 (h / holocaust))
                  :ARG0-of (n2 / need-01)))
      :ARG1 (m / monetary-quantity
            :quant 1000000
            :unit (f2 / franc
                  :mod c))
      :ARG2 (o / organization
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Restoration"
                  :op2 "Organization")
            :mod (w / world)
            :mod (r / religious-group
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Jew"))
            :purpose (s / support-01
                  :ARG0 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (s2 / survive-01
                              :ARG1 h)
                        :location (w2 / world-region
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "East"
                                    :op2 "Europe")))
                  :ARG1 (u / union
                        :mod (c2 / country
                              :name (n6 / name
                                    :op1 "Soviet")
                              :time (f3 / former)))))
      :ARG3 (c3 / city
            :name (n7 / name
                  :op1 "Jerusalem")))

            :ARG0 g2
            :ARG1 (v / vote-01
                  :ARG1 (e2 / elect-01
                        :ARG2 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
                        :ARG1-of (c2 / contest-01
                              :ARG2-of (h2 / have-degree-91

                                    :ARG3 (m / most)
                                    :ARG5 (h3 / history
                                          :poss c))))
                  :ARG2 (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (d / day))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (s / sunday)))
